## Current Visit [/currentvisit]
A single object with the current visit id, or 0 if none.

### Return current visit [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
          "id": 1, "name": "Visit 1"
        }
        
## Set current visit [/currentvisit/{id}]
Set the current visit

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Visit to set active/current (0 for none).

### Set current visit [PUT]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

            { "status": "ok" }

